trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of decoration to be added to list items.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvilken type decoration som skal legges til elementene i listen.

trans-unit.source: For information about how to develop ASP.NET mobile applications, see the [www.asp.net/mobile](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=182900) Web site.
trans-unit.target: For informasjon om hvordan du utvikler mobile ASP.NET-applikasjoner, kan du se den [www.asp.net/mobile](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=182900) webområdet.

trans-unit.source: The ListDecoration enumeration represents how you will specify decoration for a list, as bullets, numbers, or no decoration at all.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen ListDecoration representerer hvor du vil angi decoration for en liste som punkt, tall eller ingen decoration i det hele tatt.

trans-unit.source: In ASP.NET, you specify the type of decoration for a list by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.List.Decoration%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: I ASP.NET, angir typen decoration for en liste ved å angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.List.Decoration%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.List.Decoration%2A>

trans-unit.source: List items are decorated with a bullet.
